    "h_narrative_case_summary": {
      "h_1_case_narrative": "An 81-year-old female patient received Mevalotin (pravastatin sodium) 20mg  for hyperlipidemia since July 2008. The patient experienced interstitial pneumonia on 08 October 2008 (inpatient hospitalization).",
      "h_2_reporter_comments": "Although the results of DLSTs were all negative, drug-induced pneumonia was most considered from the onset of interstitial pneumonia, the condition of the shadows and the clinical course.",
      "h_4_sender_comments": "This is a spontaneously received case reported by a literature that is categorized as serious due to inpatient hospitalization. Daiichi Sankyo's assessment of the causal relationship between interstitial pneumonia and Mevalotin is related.",
      "h_5_r_case_summary_reporter_comments_native_language": [
        {
          "h_5_r_1a_case_summary_reporter_comments_text": "DLSTの結果は陰性であるが間質性肺炎の発症時期、陰影の性状、経過からも薬剤性肺炎が最も考えられる。原因薬剤は特定できていない。",
          "h_5_r_1b_case_summary_reporter_comments_language": "JA"
        }
      ]
